  "title": "Junior Business Development Executive (Training Provided)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will follow up on leads and identify new business opportunities by understanding client needs and proposing suitable solutions. You will coordinate with clients and China factories from sample to mass production, manage the sales process including forecasts and deal closure, maintain client relationships with ongoing support, and handle sales reporting and administrative tasks.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Follow up on provided leads and identify new business opportunities to expand client base</li><li>Analyze client needs and propose tailored solutions to meet their requirements</li><li>Coordinate communication and production schedules with clients and China factories from sample approval to mass production</li><li>Manage the sales process by preparing forecasts, negotiating deals, and closing sales effectively</li><li>Maintain and strengthen client relationships through regular support and communication</li><li>Prepare and submit basic sales reports and perform related administrative tasks accurately</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Proficiency in Mandarin to liaise effectively with China-based teams</li><li>Willingness to learn and grow within the role, with no prior experience required</li><li>Ability to travel overseas frequently to support business needs</li><li>Possession of a Class 3 driving licence is preferred; owning a car is a plus</li><li>Basic knowledge or interest in the Electronics/Electrical field</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills to engage with clients and internal teams</li></ul>",
